            <abstract>
                <gco:CharacterString>This spatial dataset (abs-res-mcj_FunctionalBoundaries_Current.shp) contains surveyed boundaries that are maintained by the Highlands County Property Appraisers Office. Boundaries are housed within the Highlands County Tax Parcel publicly available Tax Parcel geodatabase.</gco:CharacterString>
            </abstract>
            <purpose>
                <gco:CharacterString>This spatial data resource is to be used as the current determinate boundaries for Archbold Biological Station, Archbold Reserve, and the Lake Wales Ridge Wildlife and Environmental Area (LWRWEA) McJunkin Tract.</gco:CharacterString>
            </purpose>
